title: Flight Simulator 2020 - World Update V - Helsinki
description:
In this video we will fly to Helsinki and have a look at all POI's which have been added as part of World Update V to MSFS 2020. Helsinki has a few POI's several related to sport and 2 cathedrals. In addition there is one additional POI Suomenlinna which looks to be a very old construction but if you have more info about it feel free to add it to the comment section.
